Package: hfsubset
Title: Lightweight subsetter for hydrofabric files
Version: 0.2
Authors@R: 
     person(
      given = "Mike", 
      family = "Johnson", 
      email = "mjohnson@lynker.com", 
      role = c("aut", "cre"),
    )
Description: A lightweight, dependency-minimal subsetter for hydrofabric
    products. Given an origin feature (flowpath id, COMID, or hydrolocation
    reference), it traverses the network upstream and extracts the contributing
    flowpaths, divides, nexuses, and related layers from a GeoPackage or
    GeoParquet store.
